 their bullshit out loud, if front of cameras, every time and everywhere.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/D48ptJ4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Hathor2022]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Kids hunger for knowledge</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6qPZTiU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JuZbbPw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6qPZTiU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Herebychoice]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hello from Ireland</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZrDsfAs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NiqsBzg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZrDsfAs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[spookkoops]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bittersweet AF</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NYRaHvw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O5O6KCm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Holy balls, I'll miss her. But she's getting out of this shit hole, going someplace where she'll have healthcare, where my grandkids will never know what an active shooter drill is, cheap/free higher education, and enough English speakers not to isolate her while she learns Dutch.

It's the 5th happiest country according to the World Happiness Report. She has a job waiting, a gorgeous flat for the pair of them, and I love her husband and know he'll be extraordinarily good to her.

But she'll be so far away. I don't know what I'm gonna do without my Monkey.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NYRaHvw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hahway]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Part II + Bonus...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UbmlIgr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xTakBap.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Part I</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/14pXdhf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Part II</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3H8TP6f.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bonus I</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xYR2rHL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bonus II</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UbmlIgr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MauroChanique]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I’ve made my choice</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9qU5LJh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rLcH50P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9qU5LJh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LimJahey504]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Family first</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QS8SPWR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VwfzNmn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QS8SPWR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vtrvcr]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sugar pulling machine</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IjPmWng</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/USPVxKz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IjPmWng</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HotCoffee95